<lb n="0458c20" ed="J"/><cb:juan n="4" fun="close"><cb:jhead>月幢了禪師語錄卷四<note place="inline">終</note>　板藏嘉興楞嚴寺經坊</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>